Forget Paris;;1995;;PG-13;;Comedy,Romance;;6.5;;Billy Crystal;;Billy Crystal,Debra Winger,Joe Mantegna,Cynthia Stevenson,Richard Masur,Julie Kavner,William Hickey,Robert Costanzo,John Spencer,Tom Wright,Cathy Moriarty,Johnny Williams,Marv Albert,Bill Walton,Charles Barkley,David Robinson,Dan Majerle,Kevin Johnson;;Mickey Gordon is a basketball referee who travels to France to bury his father. Ellen Andrews, an American living in Paris, works for the airline Mickey flies on. They meet and fall in love, but their relationship goes through many difficult patches. The story is told in flashback by their friends at a restaurant waiting for them to arrive.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113097/